# Shadcn Combobox Creation Rule

## Context

- When the agent is requested to create a combobox component
- When reusable combobox functionality is needed
- When integrating shadcn/ui combobox components into the project

## Critical Rules

- Use MCP shadcn-ui-server to get combobox component details and examples
- Always check available shadcn components first using `list_shadcn_components`
- Get specific combobox component details using `get_component_details`
- Retrieve usage examples using `get_component_examples`
- Implement combobox following shadcn/ui patterns and best practices
- Make components reusable with proper TypeScript interfaces
- Include proper accessibility attributes (ARIA labels, keyboard navigation)
- Use consistent styling with TailwindCSS classes
- Implement proper error handling and loading states

